   bio:"Dr. Salami specializes in prostate cancer detection, risk stratification, and precision oncology. His laboratory research focuses on circulating tumor cells and genomic signatures that predict treatment response. He is validating gene-based prognostic tools for prostate and kidney cancers.",
   message:"I specialize in robotic surgery for prostate and kidney cancer. My approach is precision-focused: using the latest imaging and surgical technology to remove cancer while preserving the nerves and structures that matter for your recovery and quality of life.",
