   bio:"Dr. Stensland focuses on clinical trial design in urologic oncology, de-implementation of low-value cancer treatments, radiation therapy outcomes for prostate cancer, and reducing care disparities. He contributes to national efforts to improve evidence-based cancer care delivery.",
   message:"My research focuses on health disparities in cancer care — making sure every patient has equal access to the best treatment regardless of their background. I bring that same commitment to equity into my clinical practice, taking extra time to ensure every patient understands their options.",
