   bio:"Dr. Wood is a urologic oncologist at the Rogel Cancer Center\u2019s Weiser Center for Prostate Cancer. He specializes in focal therapy and emerging treatment approaches for localized prostate cancer. He is active in community health education, recently serving as keynote speaker at a Washtenaw Community College health event.",
