   bio:"Dr. Ambani is a fellowship-trained endourologist specializing in minimally invasive surgical treatment of kidney stones and upper urinary tract conditions. He performs ureteroscopy, percutaneous nephrolithotomy (PCNL), and shock wave lithotripsy, and provides comprehensive metabolic stone prevention programs.",
