   bio:"Dr. Cameron specializes in female pelvic medicine and reconstructive surgery (FPMRS), with expertise in urinary incontinence, pelvic organ prolapse, neurogenic bladder, and voiding dysfunction. She is board-certified in FPMRS and treats complex cases involving spinal cord injury, multiple sclerosis, and pelvic floor disorders. Patients consistently describe her as personable, thorough, and unhurried.",
