   bio:"Dr. Clemens is an internationally recognized expert in interstitial cystitis/bladder pain syndrome (IC/BPS), chronic pelvic pain, and lower urinary tract dysfunction. He has published extensively on the epidemiology and management of these conditions and is a leader in developing evidence-based approaches to chronic urologic pain. He holds an MSCI in clinical research methods.",
   message:"Interstitial cystitis and chronic pelvic pain are among the most challenging conditions in urology — and among the most underserved. I've spent my career studying these conditions, contributing to the AUA guidelines, and developing multimodal treatment approaches. If you've been struggling to find answers, I'm here to help.",
